It helps in provision,configure, and deploy public and private SSL/TLS certificates for use with AWS services.

ACM Provide 2 types of certificates:

1. Public (Certificates provided by ACM)
2. Private (Provided by Us, we import these)

ACM can handle multiple domains,subdomains and wild card domains


ACM can be attached to following services:
1. LoadBalancer
2. CloudFront
3. API Gateway
4. Elastic BeanStalk



Internet -> Route 53 -> ELB(ALB) -> EC2 Instances

Till the ELB communication will be secure, i.e communication will be encripted. From then ELB to EC2, it is insecure